title: United Kingdom 3 Month Bill Yield
description: UK 3 Month Bond Yield was 2.81 percent on Tuesday November 8, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United Kingdom 3 Month Bill Yield reached an all time high of 5.78 in October of 2007. This page includes a chart with historical data for UK 3M.
